[[Gonyazhinji]] (Polygon): KuChirungu izwi rokuti "polygon" rinoreva chiumbwa chine mativi mazhinji uye hawa kana kuti gonya zhinji. Mitsetse inobatana muhawa inenge yakati twasa. Shoko rinoti "poly" rinoreva "many" - kuwanda. Shoko rinoti "gon" rinobva pashoko rekuti "gonia" (Latin) rinoreva "bend" kana kuti "ankle". Isu kuChiShona tichapa zita rokuti [[Gonyazhinji]] kududzira shoko rokuti "polygon". Zvichinge zvamira nenzira iyoyi hazvichanetsi kupa mazita eShona kuzviumbwa; tinenge toverenga kuti chiumbwa chine gonya (hawa) ngani kana kuti mativi mangani.

Triangle ine mativi matatu inenge yonzi [[gonyanhatu]].
Quadrilateral ine mativi mana inenge yonzi [[gonyaina]].
Pentagon ine mativi mashanu inenge yonzi [[gonyashanu]].
Tinoramba tichienda kusvika decagon ine mativi gumi ichinzi [[gonyagumi]] zvichingodaro.

Tichiri ipapo zvakafanira kuti tionesane kuti [[gonyazhinji]] rega-rega rakaumbwa riine mativi anoverengwa kuenzana nehawa (gonya) dziri mukati mechiumbwa ichocho. Tinogona zvakare kutsiva shoko rokuti gonyazhinji nerokuti ''hawazhinji'' tochiverenga mativi echiumbwa sezviri pamusoro.
